      "lang": "javascript",
      "content": "'use strict';\n\nasync function f() {\n  return 10; // vira Promise.resolve(10)\n}\n\nasync function g() {\n  throw new Error('boom'); // vira Promise.reject\n}\n\nf().then(console.log);\ng().catch((e) => console.log(e.message));",
